r%20a%20year%20to%20help%20us%20settle%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295067438-886f-4b0e-971c-f2abbc0f05a7%5C%22%3EI%20moved%20in%20when%20I%20was%2019%20and%20she%20was%2081%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandmother%20lived%20in%20a%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20when%20I%20moved%20in%20with%20her.%20Besides%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-standing-desk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20computer%20and%20a%20desk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20only%20had%20to%20bring%20my%20clothes.%20I%20paid%20her%20for%20my%20parking%20spot%20in%20the%20building%20and%20helped%20keep%20the%20place%20tidy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20we%20were%20so%20close%20and%20had%20lived%20together%20before%2C%20there%20wasn't%20much%20adjusting%20for%20us%20to%20do.%20The%20one%20issue%20we%20had%20was%20with%20me%20going%20out%20at%20night%3B%20she%20couldn't%20understand%20how%20I%20could%20be%20out%20until%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%20and%20still%20make%20it%20to%20class%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20setup%20was%20beneficial%20for%20both%20of%20us.%20Even%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-argentina-have-more-freedom-to-be-themselves-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20Argentina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20hadn't%20lived%20there%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%20Having%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20land%20helped%20me%20focus%20on%20studying%20and%20making%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20came%20home%2C%20my%20grandmother%20had%20dinner%20ready%2C%20and%20we%20would%20spend%20time%20catching%20up%20and%20talking.%20When%20she%20needed%20to%20go%20to%20the%20doctor%2C%20I%20would%20go%20with%20her%20to%20ensure%20she%20understood%20everything%20they%20were%20telling%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c4f9e40-2c32-4df6-8654-95bf9c97b3e0%5C%22%3EPeople%20in%20my%20life%20thought%20it%20was%20weird%20at%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20not%20everyone%20understood%20my%20decision.%20My%20uncle%20told%20my%20mother%20that%20it%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-learned-living-with-my-jewish-grandparents-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eteenager%20to%20live%20with%20their%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20friends%2C%20who%20still%20mostly%20lived%20with%20their%20parents%2C%20also%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20weird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20years%20went%20by%2C%20people%20in%20my%20life%20started%20to%20see%20how%20beneficial%20it%20was%20for%20both%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20time%2C%20my%20grandmother%20confused%20her%20pills%20and%20took%20the%20wrong%20amount%20of%20her%20blood%20pressure%20medication.%20She%20called%20for%20me%2C%20dizzy%2C%20saying%20something%20was%20wrong.%20I%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20where%20we%20were%20told%20it%20was%20just%20a%20scare%20and%20that%20her%20symptoms%20would%20subside%20once%20the%20medicine%20left%20her%20system.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20college%20boyfriend%20broke%20up%20with%20me%20out%20of%20the%20blue%2C%20she%20held%20me%20while%20I%20sobbed%20into%20her%20shoulder.%20She%20scratched%20my%20back%20until%20I%20fell%20asleep%2C%20just%20like%20she%20did%20when%20I%20was%20a%20little%20girl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f320825-50f8-412b-981c-7bf2c77046b8%5C%22%3EI%20moved%20out%20after%20college%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduation%2C%20I%20moved%20out%20to%20live%20by%20myself%2C%20not%20far%20from%20her.%20I%20still%20took%20her%20to%20lunch%20with%20our%20family%20and%20made%20sure%20to%20be%20as%20present%20as%20I%20could%20be%20in%20her%20life.%20Years%20later%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20but%20still%20called%20her%20weekly%20to%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandmother%20died%20when%20she%20was%2097%2C%20seven%20years%20ago.%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20coming%2C%20so%20I%20flew%20from%20New%20York%20to%20say%20goodbye%20in%20person%20and%20t