ramell%20Tillman%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEthan%20dives%20down%20to%20the%20wreck%20and%20eventually%20retrieves%20the%20source%20code%20after%20a%20painstakingly%20long%20sequence%20in%20which%20he%20has%20to%20navigate%20falling%20missiles%20and%20debris%20while%20the%20sub%20slowly%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20intense%20moment%20sees%20him%20escape%20through%20a%20tiny%20missile%20tube%20and%20float%20to%20the%20surface.%20He%20actually%20drowns%20in%20his%20ascent%2C%20but%20luckily%2C%20Grace%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmission-impossible-pom-klementieff-hayley-atwell-helped-create-roles-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHayley%20Atwell%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20waiting%20with%20the%20inflatable%20hyperbaric%20chamber%20that%20stops%20him%20from%20dying%20from%20decompression%20sickness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20gang%20heads%20to%20a%20secure%20digital%20bunker%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20where%20the%20Entity%20is%20planning%20to%20wait%20out%20the%20impending%20nuclear%20apocalypse%20by%20combining%20its%20source%20code%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20tech%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BPoison%20Pill.%26quot%3B%20This%20would%20isolate%20the%20AI%20into%20a%20single%20hard%20drive%20and%20avert%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20they%20can%20do%20so%2C%20Gabriel%20shows%20up%20to%20try%20to%20take%20the%20Entity%20for%20himself.%20He%20reveals%20a%20smaller%20nuclear%20bomb%20will%20go%20off%20if%20Ethan%20doesn't%20give%20him%20the%20Poison%20Pill.%20Predictably%2C%20the%20deal%20goes%20south%2C%20and%20Ethan%20chases%20Gabriel%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20the%20villain%20takes%20to%20the%20sky%20in%20a%20biplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEthan%20climbs%20aboard%20a%20second%20plane%20piloted%20by%20Gabriel's%20henchman%2C%20and%20a%20jaw-dropping%20feat%20of%20aerial%20stuntwork%20ensues%2C%20as%20Ethan%20moves%20between%20the%20two%20planes%20in%20midair%20to%20retrieve%20the%20hard%20drive.