0%99s%20expense%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20have%20made%20an%20impressive%20environmental%20dent.%20Since%20their%20inception%20in%202016%2C%20Bare%20Necessities%20has%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESold%20over%20241%2C805%20products%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESaved%20more%20than%2068.8%20million%20units%20of%20single-use%20plastic%20from%20entering%20the%20environment%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDiverted%20over%20155%2C816%20kilograms%20of%20waste%20from%20landfills%20and%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Formulations%20of%20the%20products%20are%20developed%20and%20tested%20in%20a%20small%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab%20within%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20office%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T111505.688_11zon-1747892720-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t