%2Fenactus-dcac-helping-people-with-disabilities-adaptive-clothing-empowering-disabled-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskills%20and%20confidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20serve%20her%20well%20in%20the%20future.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20joined%2C%20I%20started%20learning%20to%20make%20the%20%E2%80%98Soak%20It%20Up%E2%80%99%20moisturiser%20and%20soaps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20can%20make%20deodorants%2C%20lip%20balms%2C%20and%20shampoo%20bars%2C%20and%20I%20even%20train%20others.%20It%20has%20been%20such%20a%20beautiful%20journey.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20reflects%20on%20how%20the%20company%20has%20shifted%20her%20values.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20learnt%20so%20much%20about%20sustainability%2C%20and%20I%20never%20waste%20food%20or%20water%20now.%20I%20see%20every%20resource%20as%20precious.%20Bare%20Necessities%20taught%20me%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20that%2C%20it%20gave%20her%20community.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20women%20here%20are%20amazing.%20Everyone%E2%80%99s%20so%20grounded%20and%20compassionate.%20It%20helped%20me%20see%20that%20I%20am%20not%20alone%20in%20my%20struggles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20production%20and%20warehouse%20team%20of%20the%20startup%20is%20100%25%20women-run%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453-300x157.j